description: Sunny east side condo only one block from the beach! Enter into an open living room with large oversized windows & hardwood floors. A well-appointed kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, updated backsplash & custom cabinetry. The bathroom includes a new vanity, modern fixtures and in-unit washer/dryer. A spacious bedroom offers two large closets and space for that sought after work from home desk. Access your private deck, perfect for a small bistro table, as well as a dedicated area out back for a BBQ. Additional amenities include; central air & storage in the basement. A wonderful opportunity to own in Southie!
